fulltitle: MAX ROACH-PART-4-JAZZ AND EUROPEAN CLASSICAL MUSIC
description:
This is an exclusive interview with Jazz Percussionist, Max Roach. Max was interviewed by Visual Artist, Jomo Cheatham, 30 May 1993, at The Jazz Showcase in Chicago, Illinois. Max compares European Classical music to American Classical music, called Jazz. Max also speaks about the imperialistic approach to European Classical music.   Max Roach made his transition on 16 August 2007.
